  <brief_title>Caphosol for the Reduction of Mucositis in Patients Receiving Radiation Therapy for Head and Neck Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Caphosol for the Reduction of Mucositis in Patients Receiving Radiation Therapy for Head and Neck Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
